rsa = RSA_new();
BN_hex2bn(&rsa->n, keybufA);
BN_hex2bn(&rsa->e, keybufB);

Bob can then use rsa* to publicly encrypt the symmetric cypher key which can then be sent to Alice. Alice can then decrypt with the private key
